          Experiencia
          <div
            class='w-24 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-purple-500 mx-auto mt-4 rounded-full'
          >
          </div>
        </h2>

        <div class='relative'>
          <!-- L칤nea central del timeline (desktop) -->
          <div
            class='hidden md:block absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-1 h-full bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-500 to-purple-500 rounded-full z-10'
          >
