        </p>

        <div class='flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4'>
          <a
            href='mailto:tu@email.com'
            class='flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white rounded-lg transition-colors font-medium'
          >
            <svg
              class='w-5 h-5 mr-2'
              fill='none'
              stroke='currentColor'
              viewBox='0 0 24 24'
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap='round'
